creditline: Gift of Elizabeth, Julie, and Catherine Andrus in memory of John and Marion Andrus
inscription:
Signature, Stamp

graphite mark on verso, resembling two 8's on top of each other
markings: violet stamp on verso, LL: Albert van Loock, Lugt 3751
provenance: Albert van Loock (born 1917), Lugt 3751, Brussels. John E. Andrus III, Wayzata, Minn.; by descent to his daughters, Elizabeth, Katie, and Julie; gave to MIA, 2015. Earlier provenances have been gathered, but further research will increase our knowledge of their histories.
title: Eve with the Serpent
